            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="3000" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>NETRA (नेत्र) is an AI-powered autonomous drone response system for Indian urban safety. When an incident is detected, the nearest drone is auto-dispatched within seconds, delivering a live aerial feed and GPS coordinates to emergency responders.</a:t>
            </a:r>
