            </a:pPr>
            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" altLang="en-US" sz="3000" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>System architecture: (1) Public landing page — 5-scene scroll-driven cinematic intro. (2) Real-time command dashboard — Leaflet city map, 8-drone fleet tracker, live video feeds with AI detection overlays, incident management and analytics.</a:t>
            </a:r>
          </a:p>
